flavor_text_entries.diamond:
It observes prey while hanging
inverted from branches. When the
chance presents itself, it swoops!
flavor_text_entries.pearl:
It observes prey while hanging
inverted from branches. When the
chance presents itself, it swoops!
flavor_text_entries.platinum:
If it succeeds in catching even a
faint breeze properly, it can circle
the globe without flapping once.
flavor_text_entries.heartgold:
Its flight is soundless. It uses its
lengthy tail to carry off its prey...
Then its elongated fangs do the rest.

flavor_text_entries.legends-arceus:
It glides soundlessly on pitch-black wings and sinks sharp fangs
into the throat of its prey. It takes on a look of satisfaction once
it has entirely drained its prey of blood.
